      "rationale": "The surrogate employs a graph neural network with message-passing over the pump geometry graph, trained on hemolysis index labels derived from the Giersiepen power-law model applied to CFD shear-stress histories. Architecture selection (3 message-passing layers, 128 hidden units) was justified by ablation study on the validation set. Model form is assessed at Gradation 2."
