    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-lead",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required Gradation levels for MRL 2. The ML surrogate achieves R² = 0.981 on the nominal hold-out test set and maximum bench deviation of 6.8 %, both within acceptance thresholds. The single out-of-distribution data point reported (6.8 L/min, error 4.1 %) is cited in the evidence package as confirmation that the model generalizes beyond its training domain. On this basis the credibility assessment team concluded that the surrogate is sufficiently credible for the intended COU and accepted the package at Medium assurance level.",
